<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="apparently-adv">apparently <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'pærəntli/    美 /ə'pærəntli/  </p>
<p>[句子副词]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>看来 (好像)；显然；据说：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I thought she had retired, but apparently she hasn’t.
我以为她退休了，但显然她还没有。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I wasn’t there, but apparently the concert was amazing.
我当时不在场，但据说音乐会很精彩。</p></div></div>